{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You won't be playing <i>TavernQuest</i>. You're running it. You're behind the scenes, overseeing the inner workings of the game for another player named STEVE. Can you guide STEVE away from his poor decisions so he can save the princess?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/extras/description01.png?t=1737748444\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Run TavernQuest</i> is styled after old school text adventure games, but you won't be typing. Instead, STEVE is the player and he types commands to you, often very bizarre ones. Your job is to interpret his words and choose how the adventure proceeds. The choices you make can lead him down drastically different paths, but it's ultimately up to STEVE to win the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/extras/description02.png?t=1737748444\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully narrated by the very talented Jack Dundon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control the environment and every NPC as they respond to STEVE's stupid commands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in text-based combat where your goal is to lose every time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable font and grayscale mode for enhanced readability</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737748444","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/page.bg.jpg?t=1737748444","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737748444","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/808610/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=17377